overview: Icon Male's sexy massage therapists return in Volume 3 to help hot, closeted gay men face their true sexuality. Muscular Jessie Colter gets to the bottom of 'straight' guy Andrew Fitch's tension and anxiety, while stunning Adonis Theo Ford saves athletic Alex Greene from marrying into a life of frustration. Andrew Fitch returns to give brooding stud Colton Grey some much-needed sexual healing, while Brock Avery seduces uptight corporate lawyer Rob Yaeger.
